---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Professional Loan for Doctors, CAs, Engineers & Lawyers | TrueCred Loan Expert">

<!-- Page Hero -->
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="breadcrumb">
        <a href="/">Home</a>
        <span class="sep"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i></span>
        <a href="#">Loans</a>
        <span class="sep"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i></span>
        <span>Professional Loan</span>
      </div>
      <h1>Professional Loan</h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">Specialized loans for qualified professionals — doctors, chartered accountants, engineers, architects, and lawyers — to set up or expand their practice. Get up to ₹50 lakhs without collateral at preferential interest rates starting from 10.75% p.a.</p>
      <div class="hero-highlights">
        <div class="highlight-item">
          <i class="fas fa-indian-rupee-sign"></i>
          <span>Loan Amount: ₹2L - ₹50L</span>
        </div>
        <div class="highlight-item">
          <i class="fas fa-calendar-days"></i>
          <span>Tenure: 1-7 Years</span>
        </div>
        <div class="highlight-item">
          <i class="fas fa-percent"></i>
          <span>Interest: 10.75% onwards</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Page Content -->
  <section class="page-content">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="content-grid">

        <!-- Main Content -->
        <div class="content-main">
          <h2>What is a Professional Loan?</h2>
          <p>A professional loan is a specialized financing product designed for qualified professionals like doctors (MBBS, BDS, MD, MS), chartered accountants, company secretaries, architects, engineers, lawyers, and other licensed practitioners. These loans are tailored to fund the establishment, expansion, or modernization of professional practices — from setting up a clinic or office to purchasing medical equipment, hiring staff, or renovating workspace.</p>
          <p>At TrueCred Loan Expert, we understand that professionals have unique financial needs and strong earning potential. Our partner banks and NBFCs offer preferential terms for professionals, including higher loan amounts (up to ₹50 lakhs unsecured), lower interest rates, longer tenures, and flexible repayment options including moratorium periods for fresh graduates setting up practice. Over 3,000 professionals have funded their dreams through our platform.</p>

          <div class="info-grid">
            <div class="info-box">
              <span class="info-value">10.75%</span>
              <span class="info-label">Interest Rate (p.a.)</span>
            </div>
            <div class="info-box">
              <span class="info-value">₹50 Lakh</span>
              <span class="info-label">Max Loan Amount</span>
            </div>
            <div class="info-box">
              <span class="info-value">7 Years</span>
              <span class="info-label">Max Tenure</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <h3>Professional Loan Interest Rates — April 2026</h3>
          <table class="rate-table">
            <thead>
              <tr>
                <th>Bank / NBFC</th>
                <th>Interest Rate (p.a.)</th>
                <th>Processing Fee</th>
                <th>Max Tenure</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
              <tr>
                <td>SBI</td>
                <td>10.75% onwards</td>
                <td>Up to 1.00%</td>
                <td>7 Years</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>HDFC Bank</td>
                <td>11.50% onwards</td>
                <td>Up to 2.00%</td>
                <td>5 Years</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>Axis Bank</td>
                <td>11.25% onwards</td>
                <td>Up to 1.50%</td>
                <td>7 Years</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>Kotak Mahindra Bank</td>
                <td>11.75% onwards</td>
                <td>Up to 2.00%</td>
                <td>5 Years</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>IDFC FIRST Bank</td>
                <td>12.00% onwards</td>
                <td>Up to 2.50%</td>
                <td>5 Years</td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>

          <h3>Eligibility Criteria</h3>
          <ul class="feature-list">
            <li><i class="fas fa-circle-check"></i> Qualified professional with recognized degree — MBBS, BDS, CA, CS, B.Arch, B.E./B.Tech, LLB etc.</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-circle-check"></i> Valid license or registration from professional regulatory body</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-circle-check"></i> Minimum 1 year of practice experience (waived for fresh graduates at select banks)</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-circle-check"></i> Age between 24 and 65 years at the time of loan maturity</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-circle-check"></i> CIBIL score of 700 or above for competitive interest rates</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-circle-check"></i> Annual income of ₹3,00,000 or above from professional practice</li>
          </ul>

          <h3>How to Get a Professional Loan</h3>
          <div class="steps-grid">
            <div class="step-card">
              <div class="step-num">1</div>
              <h4>Verify Qualification</h4>
              <p>Enter your professional qualification and registration details to check eligibility for preferential professional loan rates.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="step-card">
              <div class="step-num">2</div>
              <h4>Choose Loan Purpose</h4>
              <p>Select whether you need funds for practice setup, equipment purchase, working capital, or expansion. This helps match the right product.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="step-card">
              <div class="step-num">3</div>
              <h4>Submit Credentials</h4>
              <p>Upload your professional degree, registration certificate, income proof, and practice documents digitally.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="step-card">
              <div class="step-num">4</div>
              <h4>Get Funded</h4>
              <p>Receive approval within 48 hours and funds in your account within 3-5 days. Some lenders offer moratorium on EMIs for 3-6 months.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <h3>Documents Required</h3>
          <ul class="feature-list">
            <li><i class="fas fa-circle-check"></i> Professional degree certificate — MBBS, CA, LLB, B.Arch, etc.</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-circle-check"></i> Registration with professional body — Medical Council, ICAI, Bar Council, etc.</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-circle-check"></i> Practice establishment proof — clinic/office address, registration, license</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-circle-check"></i> Last 2 years ITR with computation of income from profession</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-circle-check"></i> Last 6 months bank statements of practice/professional account</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-circle-check"></i> KYC documents — Aadhaar, PAN, passport-size photographs</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Sidebar -->
        <div class="content-sidebar">
          <div class="sidebar-card">
            <h3><i class="fas fa-file-signature"></i> Apply for Professional Loan</h3>
            <form class="sidebar-form" onsubmit="return false;">
              <div class="form-group">
                <input type="text" class="form-input" placeholder="Full Name" required>
              </div>
              <div class="form-group">
                <input type="tel" class="form-input" placeholder="Mobile Number" maxlength="10" required>
              </div>
              <div class="form-group">
                <select class="form-input" required>
                  <option value="" disabled selected>Loan Amount</option>
                  <option value="200000">₹2,00,000</option>
                  <option value="500000">₹5,00,000</option>
                  <option value="1000000">₹10,00,000</option>
                  <option value="1500000">₹15,00,000</option>
                  <option value="2000000">₹20,00,000</option>
                  <option value="3000000">₹30,00,000</option>
                  <option value="5000000">₹50,00,000</option>
                </select>
              </div>
              <div class="form-group">
                <input type="text" class="form-input" placeholder="City" required>
              </div>
              <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary btn-block" style="width:100%;justify-content:center;">
                Apply Now <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i>
              </button>
            </form>
          </div>

          <div class="sidebar-card">
            <h3><i class="fas fa-link"></i> Quick Links</h3>
            <div class="sidebar-links">
              <a href="/pages/business-loan"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i> Business Loan</a>
              <a href="/pages/home-loan"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i> Home Loan</a>
              <a href="/pages/loan-against-property"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i> Loan Against Property</a>
              <a href="/pages/gold-loan"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i> Gold Loan</a>
              <a href="/pages/education-loan"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i> Education Loan</a>
              <a href="/pages/car-loan"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i> Car Loan</a>
              <a href="/pages/credit-cards"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i> Credit Cards</a>
              <a href="/pages/credit-score"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i> Credit Score</a>
              <a href="/pages/calculators"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i> EMI Calculator</a>
              <a href="/pages/insurance"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i> Insurance</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ Section -->
  <section class="faq-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <span class="section-tag">Got Questions?</span>
        <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
        <p>Common questions about professional loans.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-list">
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question">
            Which professionals are eligible for a professional loan?
            <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <div class="faq-answer-inner">
              Professional loans are available for doctors (MBBS, BDS, MD, MS, MDS, DM), chartered accountants, company secretaries, cost accountants, architects, engineers (B.E./B.Tech), lawyers (LLB, LLM), management consultants (MBA), dentists, physiotherapists, and other recognized professionals. Some lenders also extend to veterinarians, pharmacists, and alternative medicine practitioners.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question">
            Can a fresh graduate get a professional loan?
            <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <div class="faq-answer-inner">
              Yes, several banks offer professional loans to fresh graduates with special terms. SBI's doctor loan scheme, for example, provides up to ₹10 lakhs to fresh MBBS graduates to set up practice with a moratorium of up to 12 months before EMI starts. CA and lawyer loans are also available for fresh pass-outs at some NBFCs. Higher amounts become available once practice income is established.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question">
            Is collateral required for a professional loan?
            <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <div class="faq-answer-inner">
              Most professional loans up to ₹50 lakhs are unsecured and do not require collateral. Lenders trust the earning potential and stability of qualified professionals. For amounts above ₹50 lakhs (available for doctors and some specialists), collateral in the form of property or the equipment being purchased may be required. Government schemes like Stand-Up India offer additional guarantee support.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question">
            What can I use a professional loan for?
            <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <div class="faq-answer-inner">
              Professional loans can be used for: setting up a new practice (clinic, office, chamber), purchasing equipment (medical devices, diagnostic machines, IT infrastructure), renovating or expanding existing practice, hiring staff and paying initial salaries, purchasing practice from a retiring professional, pursuing higher education or specialized training, and working capital for running practice expenses.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question">
            How is a professional loan different from a business loan?
            <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <div class="faq-answer-inner">
              Professional loans offer better terms than standard business loans because lenders consider professionals lower risk due to their specialized skills and steady income. Benefits include: lower interest rates (10.75% vs 12%+), higher unsecured amounts (up to ₹50L vs ₹25L), longer tenure options (up to 7 years), moratorium facility for fresh graduates, and reduced documentation. Some banks have dedicated professional loan departments.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Page CTA -->
  <section class="page-content" style="padding-top:0;">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="page-cta">
        <div>
          <h3>Fund Your Professional Practice Today</h3>
          <p>Get up to ₹50 lakhs without collateral for doctors, CAs, lawyers, and other professionals. Rates from 10.75% p.a.</p>
        </div>
        <a href="#" class="btn btn-outline" style="color:#fff;border:2px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.5);padding:14px 32px;font-size:0.95rem;">
          Apply Now <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Footer -->

</BaseLayout>
